headline: Citizens M&A Outlook Finds Dealmaker Sentiment at a Five-Year High
summary: PROVIDENCE, R.I., January 08, 2025--Optimism about the dealmaking environment has reached a five-year high, according to Citizens’ 2025 M&A Outlook. The 14th annual survey of 400 leaders at U.S. middle-market companies and private equity firms revealed that 54% of decision-makers believe the current M&A environment is strong.
